{"tid":2232804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★中原及利嘉閣分行被惡意滋擾 已報警處理","createTime":"2020-10-06T15:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T07:20:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0109cfe9d024c732074ca2acba2b799974d6f8","tid":2232804,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"昨日早上，中原及利嘉閣於尖沙嘴柯士甸道一帶的分行，被惡意滋擾，並被人於鋪面上，張貼美聯工商舖的租售街招，中原發言人稱，其兩間分行均被貼上街招，已報警處理，將從民事及刑事方向追討一切損失。<br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣總裁廖偉強表示，該行已於昨早報警處理，同時交由公司相關部門跟進，同時保留一切投訴及追究的權利。<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1390761/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%A9%E5%98%89%E9%96%A3%E5%88%86%E8%A1%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1390761%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2596%25A3%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%25BB%258B%25E6%2593%25BE&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=1c70a259\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F1390761%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%2596%25A3%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2583%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%25BB%258B%25E6%2593%25BE&h=a996d22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/1390761/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%A9%E5%98%89%E9%96%A3%E5%88%86%E8%A1%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE</a>"},{"pid":"a71a46c8fca4037c12293f3f1138c4fc1e4ffd2d","tid":2232804,"uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/st/fcc6a